    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Easy Japanese Hiragana</strong> makes learning Japanese simple and fun!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whether you're starting from scratch or brushing up on your hiragana knowledge, this is your journey.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269120/extras/f1a132e81d33a089510cb0611aaba386.webp?t=1731681425\" width=210 height=25 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Travel from scenic Hokkaido all the way to the bustling streets of downtown Tokyo.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You'll learn all about hiragana along the way, also discovering Japanese history and culture.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Practice reading with mini-games and interactive lessons, playing with hundreds of real Japanese words to test your progress.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your friendly guide Tomomi-Chan will help you at every step, educating and motivating!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269120/extras/a507da8ef53f6f0eba0efa6a3116fd3a.webp?t=1731681425\" width=209 height=25 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Enjoy games of matching pairs, escaping mazes and piloting origami planes, all designed to practice reading hiragana while having maximum fun!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level can be replayed to strengthen your knowledge and increase your rank, until you're ready to learn new characters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use the color-code system to assist you when you're starting out, dialling up the difficulty as your confidence grows.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you've completed the campaign route, Tokyo is your playground where you can further improve your reading skills and become a true hiragana master.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3269120/extras/1b2fba25ea7ff1290bcb339d4fded5fb.webp?t=1731681425\" width=210 height=25 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Are you ready to read Japanese? Start your adventure now!</p>",
